ting atmosphere for each song\n\u25cf Weekly updates with free songs\n\u25cf Import your custom songs\n\nJoin our Discord now:  https://discord.gg/bandspace\nTalk to other players, share your custom songs, and chat directly with the developers!", "short_description": "Band Space - Demo is the lite version of the upcoming online co-op VR rhythm game. You can play drum sets, guitar, keyboard, or bass on shining stages. Team up with a band, make friends, and become a rock star! Try it now for Free!"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Cover-Portrait-1008x1440.png", "id": "3242314529236062", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75520131_3242314532569395_4127143000398014575_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=SZZJPtqPKEoQ7kNvgHtYFE-&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AkRhi0sHhMp2nQ5aABVMWbt&oh=00_AYDgqbOeHbYljTS_flq0rjdO6gwA4O4JG9u7VO7fzRyMuw&oe=66E015C5"}, {"file_name": "Hero-Cover-3000x900_New.png", "id": "2718068125034139", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75234369_2718068128367472_2174447360667117750_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=4s6xl_WxQPUQ7kNvgFz9osR&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AkRhi0sHhMp2nQ5aABVMWbt&oh=00_AYD0M-ugswKclgQv-WTRcvCHYS0Nc6PBveZ05IzZmVwz2w&oe=66E033FC"}, {"file_name": "Cover-Square-1440x1440.png", "id": "1599677630597013", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57569443_1599677633930346_8775915673430657994_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=A2mn8boO3OgQ7kNvgHu7BiS&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AkRhi0sHhMp2nQ5aABVMWbt&oh=00_AYA1DvrY7ce7Gw92VVY1KnCqmseDexNxiS3EnnT6eWIhDQ&oe=66E041B3"}, {"file_name": "Bandspace_Meta_Logo_3697x1440.png", "id": "1149661772909261", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75476759_1149661776242594_3873384865056879737_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc